{"tid":640452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓罕見發布照片 金正恩親赴醫院探視中國傷者","createTime":"2018-04-24T09:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T09:45:24.000Z","uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"373eacf58275ea76e80cf00f2e5c637509d9d611","tid":640452,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"北韓領導人金正恩到醫院看望在交通事故中受傷的中國遊客。(圖取自北韓中央通信社)<br />\n北韓領導人金正恩到醫院看望在交通事故中受傷的中國遊客。(圖取自北韓中央通信社)<br />\n北韓官媒今天報導，北韓領導人金正恩到醫院看望在交通事故中受傷的中國遊客。報導指出，金正恩專程到醫院看望受傷人員，表示北韓方面將全力救治，並配合中方做好事故善後工作。<br />\n<br />\n北韓官方媒體24日報導，北韓領導人金正恩23日前往中國大陸駐北韓大使館，對北韓發生交通意外造成數十名陸客死亡一事表達「深切」慰問。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，新華社昨晚也報導，事故發生後，中共中央、國務院高度重視。中共中央總書記、國家主席、中央軍委主席習近平立即作出重要指示，要求外交部及駐北韓使館要立即採取一切必要措施，協調北韓有關方面全力做好事故處理工作。要全力搶救受傷人員，做好遇難者善後工作。相關地方要主動開展傷亡人員家屬安撫工作。<br />\n<br />\n根據習近平指示和李克強要求，中國外交部及駐朝使館第一時間啟動應急機制，同北韓方保持密切溝通，協調全力開展救援。北韓有關部門對此高度重視，目前救援工作正在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n[img]﻿<a href=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/201804241208182342_21890.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F201804241208182342_21890.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=zVjBJXvXBebaGoQd0jZlrTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bee04f15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/201804241208182342_21890.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n金醫院在睡夢中發現撞車駁骨技術"},{"pid":"dcc74068e9d8a8aaa3ea4017495b747d9ba63480","tid":640452,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"[img]﻿<a href=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/201804241208182342_21890.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F201804241208182342_21890.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=zVjBJXvXBebaGoQd0jZlrTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bee04f15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/201804241208182342_21890.jpg[/img]</a>"},{"pid":"d306bea7ce2c9de7926be6f15a3be7b228ed4344","tid":640452,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/201804241208182342_21890.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F201804241208182342_21890.jpg&d=zVjBJXvXBebaGoQd0jZlrTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=43456cae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/201804241208182342_21890.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"17d8bde4f6d05575612b89730947bcf725e6db9a","tid":640452,"uid":2676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"又話重傷<br />\n係咪戲子黎<br />\n根本就無炒車，成單野都係吹出黎做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e2bad576e0bfa1f83ed73a6a2a264a155e0192","tid":640452,"uid":118910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d306bea7ce2c9de7926be6f15a3be7b228ed4344","tid":640452,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/201804241208182342_21890.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F201804241208182342_21890.jpg&d=zVjBJXvXBebaGoQd0jZlrTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=43456cae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/201804241208182342_21890.jpg</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"張床條杆耐撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}